REQUIREMENTS

1.) lxml (sudo apt-get install python-lxml)

INSTALLATION

1.) Copy the contents to "~/.gnome2/gedit/plugins/pastebin" except from the file 
"pastebin.gedit-plugin".

2.) Copy the file "pastebin.gedit-plugin" to "~/.gnome2/gedit/plugins" where "~" 
is your home directory. You may have to create the folder "plugins".

Restart gedit and activate the plugin in the plugins configuration.
